Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}你居然成為了超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(248,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}太讓我吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過昨天實在是讓人無法冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小千在床上直接連接的感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊想著我的事情邊撫摸著小千的身體 是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你在小千的神經連接終端裏設下病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(452,430)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過記憶棒的視聽覺模式偷窺的嗎 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也翻了她的記憶棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不是她的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女生真是難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千她比起和我在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始就更喜歡照顧你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小千選擇我的時候 我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她終於做了合乎常理的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和成績是全年級第一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道又在都大會獲勝的我交往更值吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是真心話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千一直在煩惱著 一直在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 成績和劍道的都不是你自身的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是通過Brain Burst 是加速的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前 通過劍道部主將邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(465,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是那位「青之王」的心腹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為那個人的「孩子」的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也成為了「青之王」親衛隊的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被備受期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 你現在才成為超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(540,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想和我平起平坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 你擁有我所沒有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說我是笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以你絕對贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從以前玩遊戲就沒贏過我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 那麼現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你那最後的自尊也喪失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還比不上Ash的摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 突然就開始逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓武連接全域網叫他們過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場景的情況我已經掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏懼啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏就能行使竄來竄去hit and away戰術了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 不 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(474,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的速度應該還沒被看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在對方習慣之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是很擅長玩遊戲啊 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那輕飄飄的攻擊連個屁都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千她 什麼學年第一 什麼都大會冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情根本就從來沒強求過你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千她只是希望 你能做你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你這傢伙…你這傢伙卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…太囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雨釘刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是讓你精精神神的小打鬧了一番啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真虧你幫我聚滿必殺槽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為必殺技才是對戰的亮點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你的必殺槽也差不多滿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請儘管使用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情形下 頭槌一點用都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是算了 我有拳有腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有自己的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳斷掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太弱了 你這真算是金屬色系嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴避和衝刺 已經什麼都做不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就是這樣 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是適合這種樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才 你還真是想說什麼就說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像只有自己才理解小千的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然理解 至少比你要瞭解小千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小千兩人獨處的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她突然露出哀傷的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我知道那是因為她在想你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感覺又是如何你有想過嗎 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你總是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小千都深深的陷入你這爛泥澡裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拔出來也出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我面前消失吧 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 給我和小千自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束這一切吧 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的一切 螺旋重力錘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(497,430)}<Spiral Gravity Driver>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 竟然還剩下點血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正時間也快結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了沒 各位觀戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是各位青之軍團Legion的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能繼續戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能給各位幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為點數用多了就把我拋棄掉 不覺得可惜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能給各位幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為點數用多了就把我拋棄掉 不覺得可惜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 拓武…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是絕對不能輸的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了小拓 為了小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了自己 為了黑雪姬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算再戰下去也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我沒能保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能回應你的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為…自己能夠改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的言語 你的溫柔和你的那份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是虛擬角色太弱的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為把這傢伙  白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\pos(516,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成現在這樣字的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不渴望天空 只低頭看地 只希望爬地求生存的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想去 你所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能輕鬆飛翔到的 那遙遠的天空彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更高 更遠 脫離這個猶如泥沼般的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂強大 絕對不是以結果是否勝利來衡量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂強大 並不是僅僅指獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管樣子有多難看多滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使最後被打敗倒在血泊中 身上沾滿了泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要不斷地抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算倒下也要仰望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正強大的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是沒有邊界的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全停止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跳躍 而是在飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飛行角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那對翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 白銀之鴉 是加速世界第一個飛行系角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(286,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快和總部聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你不准俯視我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我墜落吧 雷霆戰槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(499,430)}<Lighting Cyan Spike>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君 總有一天你會作為加速世界裏最快的連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(694,430)}<Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而廣為人知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後得知我們的腦和靈魂裏所秘藏的 究極的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛 飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣小春 別把我扔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要是掉下去了點數就會變成零的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我要是沒有Brain Burst的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 拜託你了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你卻要把……那個人夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐她唯一夢想完全抹殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然贏不了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一起玩的諸多遊戲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是你贏了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你承認了嗎 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是在加速世界裏 你也是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要承認嗎 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實世界裏我什麼都不如你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這裏你無論如何都贏不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們其實是對等的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以你要成為我的戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為我的同伴 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和我一樣 從今往後都作為學姐的手下而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛自己所屬的軍團Legion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破加速世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連僅有的兩個朋友都背叛了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要相信這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後 我們要把所有的事情都告訴小千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Burst的事 我們戰鬥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們一直隱藏的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把所有的事都都告訴小千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大概必須從那裏開始重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有天空與大地的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽到了你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保護了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了這樣重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 是因為學姐讓我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮 這就是你的真實姿態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 還沒有一個角色能夠實現純粹飛行能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我的預感是沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是能夠改變這個世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到了 是我該從這安穩的繭中出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次飛向天空的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做了些無聊的事呢 藍色之樁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(568,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應是你我之間的名譽之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻多次被你玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓你見識下……我真正的姿態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後如果你還期望的話 我將全力與你對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個對戰虛擬角色是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界最大背叛者黑之王 黑之睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(595,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她還繼續在玩這個遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮 雖然學姐說過十分醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 明明連與人相牽的手都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 白銀之鴉 能帶著我飛翔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 好的 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真厲害呢 真讓人著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 連接著六王軍團Legion的超頻連接者們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(578,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃黑之睡蓮 反抗僭王統治之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(339,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾與吾之軍團Legion黑暗星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在破出雌伏之網打破偽裝的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出劍 燃起火焰 戰鬥的時刻即將來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說這個還有些早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是出院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你要讓我等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 之前的木馬程序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被強制卸載了 完全用不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給拓武木馬程序的的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了點數全部扣除的處分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是程序的製作者是誰還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是善於攻破缺點的黃區那邊做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰 早晚都會將他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 一直存放在我這裏 還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看裏面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 黑雪姬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能不要只用綽號直接喊我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我不知道學姐的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 不是看這個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛拿到的時候只是稍微瞥了一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你就是你呢 春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重新做次自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說 跟綽號也沒太大區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
